    KEY Off

    Color 15, 0

    Cls

    Color 12, 1

    'Header
    Locate 1, 1
    Print Tab(80);
    Locate , 23

    Color 12
    Print "COURTSIDE COLLEGE BASKETBALL V" + GAME_VERSION$

    'Footer
    Locate 24, 1
    Print Tab(80);
    Locate , 1

